OL,6,FA police officer involved in a fracas
OL,7,Fat Manchester Airport was an
OL,8,F"uncontrolled bully with a badge", a
OL,9,Fjury has been told.
OL,11,FPC Zachary Marsden is claimed to have
OL,12,Fbeen "aggressive and uncontrolled" as
OL,13,Fhe responded to a report a member of
OL,14,Fthe public had been headbutted at a
OL,15,FStarbucks cafe in Terminal 2 arrivals
OL,16,Fjust minutes earlier on the evening of
OL,17,F23 July 2024.
