OL,6,FIt is alleged Mohammed Fahir Amaaz,
OL,7,F20, resisted as he was grabbed from
OL,8,Fbehind at a car park ticket machine
OL,9,Fwith his brother, Muhammad Amaad, 26,
OL,10,Fintervening as both inflicted a "high
OL,11,Flevel of violence" on the officers.
OL,13,FIn her closing speech at Liverpool
OL,14,FCrown Court, Chloe Gardner, defending
OL,15,FAmaad, said: "We see PC Marsden stride
OL,16,Fup to his brother's left side and grab
OL,17,Ffirst his arm and then his head and
OL,18,Fneck.
OL,26,@rD@aOUsD@RO]wD@NOU
