OL,3,CPoliceman involved in airport incident
OL,4,C'uncontrolled bully with a badge'
OL,6,F"Nothing is said by any of the
OL,7,Fofficers. No announcement of any sort.
OL,8,FNo-one says they are police officers.
OL,9,FThat's crucial.
OL,11,F"PC Marsden used unnecessary violence.
OL,12,FHis behaviour is indicative of how he
OL,13,Fbehaves in general, certainly that
OL,14,Fday. Aggressive and uncontrolled."
OL,16,FShe said Amaad was heard to say "easy,
OL,17,Feasy, easy... no, no, no" in a bid to
OL,18,Fde-escalate the situation, but his
OL,19,Fwords had "zero effect on PC Marsden"
OL,20,Fwho was "pretty much covered in red
OL,21,Fmist".
