OL,6,FMs Gardner went on: "We say that from
OL,7,Fthe outset, PC Marsden had no regard
OL,8,Ffor procedure and acted how he wanted.
OL,9,FHis way was the only way.
OL,11,F"Mr Amaad told you his intention was
OL,12,Fsolely to get PC Marsden's hands off
OL,13,Fhis brother. Mr Amaad was clear that
OL,14,Fat no point did he try to grab PC
OL,15,FMarsden's throat."
OL,17,FShe said PC Marsden had told lies in
OL,18,Fvarious statements about his
OL,19,Finteractions with Amaad at the pay
OL,20,Fstation area.
