OL,6,FMs Gardner said: "We say it is
OL,7,Fcritical when you consider PC
OL,8,FMarsden's credibility.
OL,10,F"He has come into this courtroom and
OL,11,Fhe has lied to you."
OL,13,FShe said Amaad did "no more than was
OL,14,Fnecessary" to defend his brother and
OL,15,Fthen himself as he believed he was
OL,16,F"under attack".
OL,18,FTaser strikes were later fired at both
OL,19,Fbrothers, the court has heard, and
OL,20,Ftheir mother, Shameem Akhtar, was
OL,21,Finjured in the melee.
