OL,6,FThe defendants say PC Marsden struck
OL,7,Fher in the face with his Taser, while
OL,8,Fthe officer said he believed Amaad
OL,9,Faccidentally elbowed her.
OL,11,FMobile phone footage of the officer
OL,12,Fkicking the head of Amaaz and in a
OL,13,Fstamping motion was shared on social
OL,14,Fmedia and went viral last year.
OL,16,FMs Gardner said PC Marsden went on to
OL,17,Fkick Amaad in the stomach and to the
OL,18,Fgroin and "smack him in the head" with
OL,19,Fhis Taser.
