OL,6,FShe said: "Even when he has both
OL,7,Fbrothers immobile and the mother has
OL,8,Fbeen hit in the face and is bleeding,
OL,9,Fhe continues to assault Mr Amaad.
OL,11,F"He is an uncontrolled bully with a
OL,12,Fbadge.
OL,14,F"He defied protocol, ethics, procedure
OL,15,Fand law."
OL,17,FAmaaz is alleged to have assaulted PC
OL,18,FMarsden and Pc Lydia Ward, causing
OL,19,Fthem actual bodily harm.
