OL,6,FHe is also accused of the assault of
OL,7,Femergency worker PC Ellie Cook, and
OL,8,Fthe earlier assault by beating of a
OL,9,Fmember of the public, Abdulkareem
OL,10,FIsmaeil, at a Starbucks cafe in T2
OL,11,Farrivals.
OL,13,FAmaad is alleged to have assaulted PC
OL,14,FMarsden, causing actual bodily harm.
OL,16,FBoth defendants, from Rochdale,
OL,17,FGreater Manchester, deny the
OL,18,Fallegations and say they were lawfully
OL,19,Facting in self-defence or in defence
OL,20,Fof each other.
